hopobject.body: A packet of envelopes how many ibuprofen tablets can you take at one time At the Golden Gate National Recreation Area in the San Francisco Bay Area, park rangers were preparing to post signs at Muir Woods to turn away visitors. All ferries to Alcatraz would be canceled, absent a resolution to the budget stalemate. "The island will be closed," said Howard Levitt, director of communications for the park. "Boats will not be running there."
